Package: grpSLOPE
Type: Package
Title: Group SLOPE (Sorted L1 Penalized Estimation)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alexej", "Gossmann", email = "alexej.go@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The Group SLOPE method can be used to select groups of predictor variables
    in a linear regression model with pre-specified group structures among the predictors, 
    while controlling the (group-wise) false discovery rate at a user-specified level.
